➜公益：救助徽县江洛镇立斗村白血病患者18岁女孩陈雪
http://www.sohu.com/a/415517154_804243	32256
<p>18岁女儿不幸身患重症！她渴望战胜病魔！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200829/bb81827e284049818185e2c4d6c4a8b8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200829/04496c5853b34b918d02797382c609b2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200829/9f0bca85e4ee4e11a71e181b8e4faa18.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200829/825d1ccf6f9842f79db09dc2309890f2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
